{"tid":710650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[蘇亞雷斯] 兩男旺角站大打出手 一人遭咬甩手指","createTime":"2018-06-21T02:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T05:51:28.000Z","uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"09c40fd6cc553fb5b844651133861fa66063b291","tid":710650,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:28:42.000Z","msg":"兩男旺角站大打出手 一人遭咬甩手指<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發生兩乘客打架咬甩手指事件。早上近9時上班繁忙時間，兩名男乘客在旺角站荃灣綫方向月台，疑因事發生爭執，愈吵愈烈，兩人大打出手，其中一漢竟出動「咬人功」，噬咬對方的右手姆指，當場甩掉部份姆指，警員及救護員接報到場，幸尋回被咬甩姆指，將傷者連同甩脫的姆指一併送院進行接駁手術，兩漢同涉公眾地方打架被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180621/58344490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F58344490&d=aoqUoJv2Fu3xeYwg8hDTi26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=46fe8987\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F58344490&h=2c6d53c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180621/58344490</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/G856igMdMhPP2/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FG856igMdMhPP2%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c41d2884&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efe02bd12ec33127118a679cae70fd1b83bf425c","tid":710650,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"香港而家日日都有路人爭鬥<br />\n其實大家都充滿怨氣　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　"},{"pid":"a27a676085cf811e8441e7599e45b558df32dbb6","tid":710650,"uid":38543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6156416c56c93b55ebf47864bacc967be04701","tid":710650,"uid":113626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"咬人手指果個係咪傻架<br />\n排期